<font color=#FFFF00>Aku menyukai suasana di sini.</font>

586
00:32:18,569 --> 00:32:20,009
<font color=#FFFF00>Syukurlah kamu menyukainya.</font>

587
00:32:20,009 --> 00:32:21,109
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu sering makan di sini?</font>

588
00:32:21,109 --> 00:32:22,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Dari waktu ke waktu.</font>

589
00:32:23,839 --> 00:32:26,109
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga, wajah Nona Lee tersipu malu.</font>

590
00:32:26,509 --> 00:32:29,380
