00:35:27,860 --> 00:35:30,159
<font color=#FFFF00>kopilot Penerbangan 801</font>

640
00:35:31,230 --> 00:35:33,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Kim Bum Joon.</font>

641
00:35:35,570 --> 00:35:36,739
<font color=#FFFF00>Nona Lee.</font>

642
00:35:36,869 --> 00:35:39,539
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu tahu ada masalah</font>

643
00:35:39,840 --> 00:35:41,070
<font color=#FFFF00>dengan penambahan penerbangan Maskapai Juhan, bukan?</font>

