<font color=#FFFF00>dan kenapa kakakku</font>

662
00:36:34,960 --> 00:36:36,699
<font color=#FFFF00>terpaksa disebut pembunuh.</font>

663
00:36:41,570 --> 00:36:42,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Nona Lee.</font>

664
00:36:44,940 --> 00:36:46,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mohon kepadamu.</font>

665
00:36:49,340 --> 00:36:50,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Kumohon</font>

