<font color=#FFFF00>tolonglah kakakku.</font>

667
00:37:17,199 --> 00:37:18,239
<font color=#FFFF00>Selamat datang.</font>

668
00:37:18,239 --> 00:37:20,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada yang bisa kubantu?</font>

669
00:37:20,070 --> 00:37:23,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu Kim Young Pil,</font>

670
00:37:24,039 --> 00:37:25,380
<font color=#FFFF00>mekanik yang memeriksa</font>

671
