00:38:04,449 --> 00:38:05,619
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang akan kulakukan?</font>

682
00:38:07,320 --> 00:38:09,150
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka menemukan orang-orang itu,</font>

683
00:38:09,150 --> 00:38:11,019
<font color=#FFFF00>jadi, kita harus merebut mereka.</font>

684
00:38:16,860 --> 00:38:18,059
<font color=#FFFF00>Hai, Kepala On.</font>

685
00:38:18,630 --> 00:38:20,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Mau kita simpulkan sekarang?</font>

686
00:38:21,230 --> 00:38:22,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Hari ini pukul 13.00,</font>

687
00:38:22,400 --> 00:38:24,469
<font color=#FFFF00>Komite Penyelidikan Ulang JH 801</font>

688
00:38:24,469 --> 00:38:26,239
<font color=#FFFF00>akan mengadakan</font>

689
00:38:26,239 --> 00:38:27,469
<font color=#FFFF00>wawancara pers</font>

690
00:38:27,469 --> 00:38:29,840
<font color=#FFFF00>dan mengumumkan hasil penyelidikan ulang tersebut.</font>

691
00:38:29,840 --> 00:38:31,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Wakil Presdir</font>

