00:39:35,510 --> 00:39:37,079
<font color=#FFFF00>- Baiklah.
- Bagus.</font>

716
00:39:42,780 --> 00:39:44,150
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini menyenangkan.</font>

717
00:39:44,150 --> 00:39:46,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Sepertinya Citah menyukainya.</font>

718
00:39:46,719 --> 00:39:48,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu karena dia tua.</font>

719
00:39:48,090 --> 00:39:50,320
