<font color=#FFFF00>Aku lahir tahun 1979.</font>

721
00:39:53,989 --> 00:39:56,559
<font color=#FFFF00>Park Soon Jung usia 39 tahun.</font>

722
00:39:56,559 --> 00:39:58,199
