<font color=#FFFF00>adik kopilot JH 801</font>

749
00:41:54,880 --> 00:41:56,079
<font color=#FFFF00>Kim Bum Joon.</font>

750
00:42:08,489 --> 00:42:11,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya akan mengumumkan</font>

751
